episodes.title: The shadow side of the anti-cult movement
episodes.description: In this episode, I share some thoughts about the dark side, or shadow side of the anti-cult movement and where I feel it's gone a bit awry.I've been reflecting on this topic for a while and it feels so important to open up this conversation. My husband (Mark Vicente) also chimed in with some feisty thoughts about it all! I hope this episode can help you stay true to yourself as you navigate this crazy time.Please note: Mark uses some foul language in this episode!Instagram: @ofsoula...
